    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>PxrShadedSide is an OSL pattern that tells us which side is being shaded. This is useful for shading object with two sides where we can assign different color to each side of the object.</p><h3 id=\"PxrShadedSide-Parameters\">Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrShadedSide-Invert\">Invert</h4><p>If the side we want is on the opposite side, turn this on to invert it.</p><h3 id=\"PxrShadedSide-Example\">Example</h3><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224902/shadedside.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330621293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224902/shadedside.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330621293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224914\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shadedside.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224902\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fd591e53-8bc3-44a6-b275-1e6d7d88cfeb\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>PxrShadedSide with PxrMix for Diffuse Color</em></p>"
    }
